OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782031683
OL,3,CResidents rally to save century-old
OL,4,C'royal' trees in Lancashire
OL,6,FResidents gathered in Walton-le-Dale,
OL,7,FLancashire, to protest against plans
OL,8,Fto fell 18 historic lime trees that
OL,9,Fhave stood beside the River Ribble for
OL,10,Fmore than a century.
OL,12,FThe trees, known as the Royal Limes,
OL,13,Fwere planted in 1912 to commemorate
OL,14,Fthe coronation of King George V and
OL,15,Fhave become a cherished local landmark.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782031683
OL,3,CResidents rally to save century-old
OL,4,C'royal' trees in Lancashire
OL,6,FHowever, the Environment Agency says
OL,7,Fsome of them are obstructing the
OL,8,Fconstruction of vital new flood
OL,9,Fdefences designed to protect hundreds
OL,10,Fof homes and businesses from future
OL,11,Fflooding.
OL,13,FCampaigners argue that alternative
OL,14,Fflood protection schemes could be
OL,15,Fimplemented without removing the trees.
OL,17,FMany residents say the limes are an
OL,18,Fimportant part of the area's heritage
OL,19,Fand landscape.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782031683
OL,3,CResidents rally to save century-old
OL,4,C'royal' trees in Lancashire
OL,6,FOne local protester described the
OL,7,Ftrees as a constant presence
OL,8,Fthroughout their life, saying they
OL,9,Fcould not imagine the road without
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,FHelen Murphy said: "I'm a local. I've
OL,13,Fgrown up watching them through every
OL,14,Fseason, and I just can't imagine not
OL,15,Fthem not being there.
OL,17,F"We're here to protest. We don't want
OL,18,Fthese lovely, beautiful trees to go."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782031683
OL,3,CResidents rally to save century-old
OL,4,C'royal' trees in Lancashire
OL,6,FOthers expressed concerns that
OL,7,Falternative construction methods
OL,8,Finvolving road closures could cause
OL,9,Fsignificant disruption to transport
OL,10,Flinks and public services.
OL,12,FDamian North, the Chair of Save The
OL,13,FRoyal Lime Trees, believes there are
OL,14,Fviable alternatives. He said: "The
OL,15,FEnvironment Agency didn't know the
OL,16,Fimportance of these trees, they didn't
OL,17,Facknowledge the history, the heritage,
OL,18,Fthe Royal connection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782031683
OL,3,CResidents rally to save century-old
OL,4,C'royal' trees in Lancashire
OL,6,F"We're not arguing about the need for
OL,7,Fflood defenses, it's just the way that
OL,8,Fthey're achieved - without the need
OL,9,Ffor cutting down these trees."
OL,11,FThe Environment Agency insists that
OL,12,Fprotecting the community from flooding
OL,13,Fremains its priority and says tree
OL,14,Ffelling is considered only as a last
OL,15,Fresort.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782031683
OL,3,CResidents rally to save century-old
OL,4,C'royal' trees in Lancashire
OL,6,FAn Environment Agency Spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our priority is protecting over
OL,8,F300 Walton-le-Dale homes and
OL,9,Fbusinesses from the devastating
OL,10,Feffects of flooding and felling trees
OL,11,Fis always our last resort.
OL,13,F"We can't carry out construction from
OL,14,Fwithin the river due to the
OL,15,Fsignificant operational challenges of
OL,16,Fworking within a constantly changing
OL,17,Ftidal river environment and the risk
OL,18,Fof environmental harm to the river,
OL,19,Fits wildlife and surrounding land.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782031683
OL,3,CResidents rally to save century-old
OL,4,C'royal' trees in Lancashire
OL,6,F"Relocating the works further inland
OL,7,Fis also not feasible, as the road
OL,8,Fcarries essential utilities and
OL,9,Fregionally important communications
OL,10,Fcables.
OL,12,F"We understand the strength of feeling
OL,13,Ffor these trees and we've taken 180
OL,14,Fcuttingsthat are growing at a nursery
OL,15,Fthat we will replant in the area."
OL,17,FMore than 8,000 people have signed a
OL,18,Fpetition calling for the trees to be
OL,19,Fsaved.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
